00:42.501 --> 00:44.537
AUDREY: They're not real.

00:44.670 --> 00:46.501
—I heard Audrey's voice again.
—What'd you hear?

00:46.631 --> 00:50.340
She was talking about being trapped
inside a place that wasn't real.

00:50.468 --> 00:52.254
So you think Audrey
is still in the barn

00:52.386 --> 00:54.297
and it's still imploding?

00:55.348 --> 01:00.593
lt's dying, and unless we move fast,
it's gonna take you with it.

01:04.982 --> 01:07.724
And I rest my sleepy head

01:07.860 --> 01:10.647
upon my soft and cozy bed.

01:10.780 --> 01:13.738
I pray the Lord to keep me safe

01:13.866 --> 01:16.699
and watch me close until I wake.

01:16.827 --> 01:18.328
I love you, Harper.

01:19.372 --> 01:21.237
Sleep tight.

01:29.715 --> 01:34.800
