02:07.086 --> 02:09.452
Let's play a game.

02:23.894 --> 02:25.759
Bye—bye.

02:31.444 --> 02:33.605
Rise and shine, Harper.

02:34.071 --> 02:35.607
Harper?

02:35.740 --> 02:38.277
Oh, my God.
Harper!

02:38.409 --> 02:42.322
I went in this morning to wake her,
and she was gone.

02:42.455 --> 02:44.571
Whoever took her
had an awful laugh.

02:44.707 --> 02:46.618
Harper said that it was just
her imaginary friend,

02:46.751 --> 02:48.161
but there had to be
someone else in there.

02:48.294 --> 02:50.000
Are you sure someone
entered the house?

02:50.129 --> 02:52.666
Do you know anything
about little girls, Chief?

02:52.798 --> 02:54.914
A little.

02:55.051 --> 02:59.511
