where that is?

04:17.508 --> 04:19.248
I can't.

04:20.136 --> 04:22.502
The barn was built for you.

04:22.638 --> 04:24.629
Only you can see through this.

04:24.765 --> 04:26.676
You know what I don't get?

04:26.809 --> 04:29.972
I don't get why everybody else
disappeared and you didn't.

04:32.481 --> 04:34.017
Who are you, William?

04:34.150 --> 04:36.937
| wish I could tell you...

04:37.069 --> 04:38.058
but I can't.

04:38.195 --> 04:41.437
Right now I'm only allowed
to help you.

04:43.284 --> 04:47.994
So, do you want to see the truth?

04:52.209 --> 04:53.995
Yes.

04:54.128 --> 04:56.210
Okay.

04:56.338 --> 04:58.124
Close your eyes.
Take a deep breath.

04:59.008 --> 05:00.589
Close your eyes.

05:00.718 --> 05:03.209
Clear your mind of all expectations

05:03.345 --> 05:06.508
and tell yourself
when you open your eyes,

05:06.640 --> 05:08.972
your mind will open,

05:09.810 --> 05:13.723
and the truth will appear before you.

05:20.112 --> 05:21.022
Oh, my God.

05:22.907 --> 05:23.942
What's happening?

05:24.074 --> 05:26.611
Now you can see it.
The barn is dying.

05:26.744 --> 05:28.280
We're in its final moments.

05:28.412 --> 05:30.619
What if I can't find this door?

05:30.748 --> 05:33.956
You will cease to exist.

05:34.084 --> 05:36.336
