07:13.142 --> 07:15.804
[Cell phone rings]

07:20.316 --> 07:21.351
Yeah.

07:23.110 --> 07:24.316
Sorry. I'm not good with pressure.

07:24.445 --> 07:26.481
I know.
Look, you're doing great.

07:26.614 --> 07:29.902
Just try to keep listening.

07:30.034 --> 07:33.242
Yeah, to the magic invisible barn.

07:33.370 --> 07:35.827
Okay.

07:35.956 --> 07:37.617
It's okay.

07:41.420 --> 07:42.580
What?

07:42.713 --> 07:45.250
That was Dwight.

07:45.382 --> 07:47.919
A second kid's gone missing,
another four—year—old.

07:48.052 --> 07:51.385
But Audrey could walk out here
at any second.

07:51.513 --> 07:54.926
Usually when Jennifer hears Audrey,
she's been relaxed.

07:55.059 --> 07:58.176
Now, getting her to relax
is something that you suck at.

07:59.438 --> 08:01.178
But what don't you suck at?

08:03.651 --> 08:05.937
Solving cases, finding people.

08:06.070 --> 08:07.651
Exactly.

08:07.780 --> 08:11.614
So you go find the kids.
I will get her to calm down.

08:11.742 --> 08:14.734
We will find Audrey,
and we'll all live happ--

08:17.247 --> 08:18.453
You know what I mean.

08:20.417 --> 08:21.918
Get her to hear.

08:25.673 --> 08:27.413
