for parent—teacher day too well.

09:50.507 --> 09:52.919
You fit pretty good in mine.

09:53.051 --> 09:54.882
You're a good chief, Dwight.

09:55.012 --> 09:56.377
Thanks.

09:57.222 --> 10:00.180
Let's check the preschool,
see what these kids have in common.

10:00.309 --> 10:01.344
