Here.

11:15.717 --> 11:20.381
The idea is to allow your mind
to be as empty as the bowl.

11:21.223 --> 11:23.555
Now, close your eyes...

11:25.394 --> 11:28.306
...and take a deep breath in.

11:28.438 --> 11:29.769
[lnhales deeply]

11:34.862 --> 11:35.897
[Thuds]

11:36.780 --> 11:37.860
All right, what was that?

11:37.990 --> 11:39.196
That's good.
Okay, that's a good sign.

11:39.324 --> 11:40.404
That means someone's
looking for you.

11:40.534 --> 11:42.149
